Package main.java.embl.rieslab.emu.ui.uiproperties

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ImmutableMultiStateUIProperty
    UIProperty with a fixed number of ordered states whose values are known at compilation time.
    MultiStateUIProperty
    A UIProperty with multiple allowed states, whose values are unknown at compilation time.
    PropertyPair
    Class used to pair a UIproperty with a MMProperty.
    SingleStateUIProperty
    A UIProperty that accepts only a single state, whose value can be set by the user in the configuration wizard.
    TwoStateUIProperty
    UIProperty that only accepts two states: ON or OFF.
    UIProperty
    A UIProperty object is aimed at linking a user interface action with a MMProperty from Micro-Manager.
